HEADWORD: love-philtre
<hw>love-philtre</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos>
<def>a fabled drink credited with magical power; it can make the one who
takes it love the one who gave it.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> philter, philtre, love-potion.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

